creator: Gato Barbieri
title: Conversations With Gato Barbieri 03 07 15
description: Leandro "Gato" Barbieri Was The Featured Guess Artist on 07 March, 2015 to record The Album "Luisa" with The Black Butterflies. Reunited with former band mate Karl Berger after 50 years, turned out to be a session that will not be forgotten.
